      <title>Re: Is this the best medium for the job?</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/doc/forum/general/is_this_the_best_medium_for_the_job/re_is_this_the_best_medium_for_the_job5</link>
      <description>@ André R.&#13;
&#13;
Thank you Andre!&#13;
&#13;
Per your request I have made the following modifications.&#13;
&#13;
1. Linked to the forum topic in the forum template (this way the discussion menu link remains displayed even when within the forum / forum topic). &#13;
&#13;
2. Description ... I'm considering your request for a description / intro of the wiki entry. I'm not sure how best to implement offhand since the wiki articles do not have a short description  / intro field within the entry.&#13;
&#13;
For now I added a link within the forum template to display the name of the wiki article with return link.&#13;
&#13;
3. Thread message display order - I have also reversed the default order to display messages (as most recent) first to help avoid unnecessary scrolling or pagination and improve usability.&#13;
&#13;
4. Latest updates rss feed - I have added an rss feed with only the latest updated conteent objects on ezpedia. http://ezpedia.org/rss/updated/discussion&#13;
&#13;
5. Latest discussion (only) updates rss feed - I have added an rss feed with only the latest updated content objects on ezpedia. http://ezpedia.org/rss/updated/discussion&#13;
&#13;
6. Homepage - Layout - I have also added a list of recent discussions into the homepage layout. http://ezpedia.org/&#13;
&#13;
Take a look at the changes and let me know what you think.&#13;
&#13;
Cheers,&#13;
Heath</description>
